WEBVTT

00:00.440 --> 00:04.640
My client's curiosities are less to do with me than they are with my profession.

00:05.480 --> 00:12.220
Clients who inquire about the psychiatric field usually do so out of their own discomfort about their illness.

00:12.220 --> 00:18.080
With this client, however, her inquiries may help in her own rehabilitation.

00:19.040 --> 00:29.740
There is an undeniable chance that learning about her own condition may intensify her worries, but I think that can be avoided in our relationship.
